Project Overview

This project focuses on building an interactive sales dashboard to analyze sales trends, customer behavior, and product performance.
Using Python, Pandas, Seaborn, Matplotlib, and Plotly, the dashboard presents both static and interactive visualizations to support data-driven business decisions.

The project is designed for students and beginners, following a complete data analysis pipeline from loading data to generating insights.

